One thing I’m asking myself is to extent unemployment goes up a couple points, how much would it impact aapl / Msft / nvda etc revenue and earnings?
Probably not much

KKGB Kitty: Initial claims are gradually trending towards that key 280 K - 290 K  level that will be a clear indication, if sustained, that labor market flipped into weakness. You can ignore all the remaining chatter around frauds, Minnesota, compositional effects, etc…
